## Managing Deposits, Withdrawals, and Account Security

The financial operations within the Polymarket mobile app deserve careful attention from all users. Deposits through Apple Pay or Google Pay convert fiat currency to USDC and credit your trading balance within minutes. Bank transfers and cryptocurrency deposits offer alternatives with varying processing times. For withdrawals, the app requires completed identity verification above certain thresholds, which involves submitting government identification and proof of address. Processing times typically range from one to three business days for fiat withdrawals, though cryptocurrency withdrawals to external wallets complete within hours. Security features include biometric authentication through Face ID or fingerprint recognition, two-factor authentication options, and session management controls. The app allows you to view and terminate active sessions from other devices, an important safeguard for traders who access their accounts across multiple platforms. Regular review of connected wallet permissions and authorized applications reduces exposure to potential security vulnerabilities. You can explore market opportunities directly by visiting [Polymarket](https://polymarket.com/?r=POLYTips) through their web interface, though the mobile app provides the most convenient ongoing experience.

